{"tid":343482,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(有圖)做緊紀律部隊希望你入一入黎 有野想同你地講","createTime":"2017-08-01T13:11:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T13:42:31.000Z","uid":79111,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1f56d02c1a2f7e0ef24e5d7f78da02815f3b699b","tid":343482,"uid":79111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T13:11:49.000Z","msg":"其實只係多謝你為左香港付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能你一開始係為左高薪厚職 唔會咁易俾人炒先會投身紀律部隊<br />\n定係你其實係想為左令香港呢個社會有一點兒不一樣<br />\n又可能係自己本身好想為公眾服務<br />\n又可能係本身睇唔過眼社會某D行為先會想投身紀律部隊<br />\n希望你地唔好忘記初衷 <br />\n祝咁多位接住落黎升官發財!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講到明有圖<br />\n更係要俾D J圖大家欣賞下<br />\n即刻去圖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/210232_4c4dc09d431aaeaff4e2295ecdffdf02.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F210232_4c4dc09d431aaeaff4e2295ecdffdf02.jpg&h=7f94c846&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/210233_40ef7875b66e65ab34bc567155bdabc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F210233_40ef7875b66e65ab34bc567155bdabc2.jpg&h=e7b83728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/210234_1c38d2aca2627ba45f32d1a55904fcd1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F210234_1c38d2aca2627ba45f32d1a55904fcd1.jpg&h=8a15ad61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/01/210235_b69c6160cafb078a2f05c3301bd3fd8d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F01%2F210235_b69c6160cafb078a2f05c3301bd3fd8d.jpg&h=91a701b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https:/